# Consumer .npmrc — copy this to `.npmrc` in the root of GenX / TatvaPractice
# (or any app that installs @dhspl-tatvacare/tesseract-ui from GitHub Packages).
#
# It does two things:
#   1. Route the @dhspl-tatvacare scope to GitHub's private npm registry.
#   2. Authenticate with a GitHub token that has `read:packages` (gated by org access).
#
# Do NOT paste the token here. Reference an env var so the secret never lands in git:
#   export GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_xxx   (locally, in your shell profile)
#   in CI: expose the token as the GITHUB_TOKEN secret/env.

@dhspl-tatvacare:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com
//npm.pkg.github.com/:_authToken=${GITHUB_TOKEN}
